OL,6,FLouise Haigh is entitled to severance
OL,7,Fpay despite resigning after less than
OL,8,Fsix months as transport secretary,
OL,9,FDowning Street has said.
OL,11,FMs Haigh, the Sheffield Heeley MP,
OL,12,Fquit on Friday after it emerged she
OL,13,Fhad pleaded guilty to a criminal
OL,14,Foffence related to incorrectly telling
OL,15,Fpolice that a work mobile phone was
OL,16,Fstolen in 2013.
